e\", \"from\": 179, \"to\": 197}, {\"ngram\": \"a positive experience\", \"from\": 205, \"to\": 226}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 29-year-old has been accustomed to making history by becoming both the first Israeli man to be crowned European champion and the first to qualify in the epee for an Olympics.\", \"from\": 230, \"to\": 408, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 311, \"end\": 318, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israelis\", \"score\": 0.9947917588602382, \"rank\": 0.004990122552016615, \"text\": \"Israeli\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israelis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israelis\"}, {\"begin\": 337, \"end\": 354, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Figure_Skating_Championships\", \"score\": 0.5598692648552941, \"rank\": 0.7861249126610226, \"text\": \"European champion\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Figure_Skating_Championships\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Figure_Skating_Championships\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"history\", \"from\": 276, \"to\": 283}, {\"ngram\": \"the epee\", \"from\": 383, \"to\": 391}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympics\", \"from\": 396, \"to\": 407}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, despite being ranked seventh in Paris, Freilich went down to a surprise defeat to Italy's Andrea Santarelli, ranked some 19 places below him, in the last 32 round.\", \"from\": 410, \"to\": 582, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 451, \"end\": 456, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999999973852, \"rank\": 2.6127837998589706e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 501, \"end\": 506, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"score\": 0.819609302666447, \"rank\": 0.17937221043616616, \"text\": \"Italy\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\"}, {\"begin\": 509, \"end\": 526, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrea_Santarelli\", \"score\": 0.9999836288942273, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Andrea Santarelli\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrea_Santarelli\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrea_Santarelli\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Freilich\", \"from\": 458, \"to\": 466}, {\"ngram\": \"a surprise defeat\", \"from\": 480, \"to\": 497}, {\"ngram\": \"the last 32 round\", \"from\": 564, \"to\": 581}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Israel-born son of Australian parents was upset after losing, sobbing into the chest of one of his team's staff.\", \"from\": 584, \"to\": 700, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 607, \"end\": 617, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_cricket_team\", \"score\": 0.7766720632547308, \"rank\": 0.24305696164698357, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_cricket_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_cricket_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Israel-born son\", \"from\": 584, \"to\": 603}, {\"ngram\": \"the chest\", \"from\": 663, \"to\": 672}, {\"ngram\": \"his team's staff\", \"from\": 683, \"to\": 699}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"At the moment there is huge disappointment and I am sure it will only get stronger as time goes by,\\\" he told AFP.\", \"from\": 702, \"to\": 816, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 812, \"end\": 815, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"score\": 0.9999999147128201, \"rank\": 7.532182151311305e-08, \"text\": \"AFP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the moment\", \"from\": 706, \"to\": 716}, {\"ngram\": \"huge disappointment\", \"from\": 726, \"to\": 745}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 789, \"to\": 793}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Freilich said he was proud to have qualified for the Olympics and he at least had his family with him to provide solace, but he said his defeat was small fry in contrast to what is happening at home where Israel is engaged in a war in Gaza which threatens to spread.\", \"from\": 818, \"to\": 1084, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1023, \"end\": 1029, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"score\": 0.9999999984522674, \"rank\": 1.5188605547125681e-09, \"text\": \"Israel\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\"}, {\"begin\": 1053, \"end\": 1057, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaza_City\", \"score\": 0.91584939645383, \"rank\": 0.09188257793448402, \"text\": \"Gaza\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaza_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaza_City\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Freilich\", \"from\": 818, \"to\": 826}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 867, \"to\": 879}, {\"ngram\": \"his family\", \"from\": 900, \"to\": 910}, {\"ngram\": \"solace\", \"from\": 931, \"to\": 937}, {\"ngram\": \"his defeat\", \"from\": 951, \"to\": 961}, {\"ngram\": \"small fry\", \"from\": 966, \"to\": 975}, {\"ngram\": \"contrast\", \"from\": 979, \"to\": 987}, {\"ngram\": \"home\", \"from\": 1012, \"to\": 1016}, {\"ngram\": \"a war\", \"from\": 1044, \"to\": 1049}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am proud to represent my country and it's important for my country to see that we have Israeli athletes representing them,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1086, \"to\": 1221, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1176, \"end\": 1183, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israelis\", \"score\": 0.9947917588602382, \"rank\": 0.004990122552016615, \"text\": \"Israeli\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israelis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israelis\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my country\", \"from\": 1111, \"to\": 1121}, {\"ngram\": \"my country\", \"from\": 1145, \"to\": 1155}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think in the larger picture, if I put things in perspective, it's a positive experience.\\\"\", \"from\": 1223, \"to\": 1315, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the larger picture\", \"from\": 1235, \"to\": 1253}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 1264, \"to\": 1270}, {\"ngram\": \"perspective\", \"from\": 1274, \"to\": 1285}, {\"ngram\": \"a positive experience\", \"from\": 1292, \"to\": 1313}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Freilich refused to use the war as an excuse, although it has made training more complicated.\", \"from\": 1317, \"to\": 1410, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Freilich\", \"from\": 1317, \"to\": 1325}, {\"ngram\": \"the war\", \"from\": 1341, \"to\": 1348}, {\"ngram\": \"an excuse\", \"from\": 1352, \"to\": 1361}, {\"ngram\": \"training\", \"from\": 1384, \"to\": 1392}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It has not restricted us too much,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1412, \"to\": 1457, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1435, \"to\": 1437}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Before the war began we had sparring partners who would come with us to Israel and come train with us.\", \"from\": 1459, \"to\": 1562, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1532, \"end\": 1538, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"score\": 0.9999999984522674, \"rank\": 1.5188605547125681e-09, \"text\": \"Israel\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the war\", \"from\": 1467, \"to\": 1474}, {\"ngram\": \"partners\", \"from\": 1497, \"to\": 1505}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1526, \"to\": 1528}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1559, \"to\": 1561}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Since the war began they could not so I had to travel abroad.\", \"from\": 1564, \"to\": 1626, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the war\", \"from\": 1571, \"to\": 1578}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But that's OK.\", \"from\": 1628, \"to\": 1643, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It did not impair my preparations in any way.\", \"from\": 1644, \"to\": 1689, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my preparations\", \"from\": 1662, \"to\": 1677}, {\"ngram\": \"any way\", \"from\": 1681, \"to\": 1688}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The fact that I got here is a fantastic result.\\\"\", \"from\": 1690, \"to\": 1738, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The fact\", \"from\": 1690, \"to\": 1698}, {\"ngram\": \"a fantastic result\", \"from\": 1718, \"to\": 1736}]}, {\"sentence\": \"- 'Clear my head' - Freilich, one of six children, fell in love with fencing aged five.\", \"from\": 1740, \"to\": 1828, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my head\", \"from\": 1749, \"to\": 1756}, {\"ngram\": \"- Freilich\", \"from\": 1758, \"to\": 1768}, {\"ngram\": \"six children\", \"from\": 1777, \"to\": 1789}, {\"ngram\": \"love\", \"from\": 1799, \"to\": 1803}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He was first inspired by his father, Gabby, who won him over by telling him it was \\\"sword fighting\\\".\", \"from\": 1829, \"to\": 1929, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his father\", \"from\": 1854, \"to\": 1864}, {\"ngram\": \"Gabby\", \"from\": 1866, \"to\": 1871}, {\"ngram\": \"sword fighting\", \"from\": 1913, \"to\": 1927}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He said he immediately had visions of the movies and \\\"backflips, jumps and throwing the sword in the air and catching it\\\".\", \"from\": 1931, \"to\": 2053, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"visions\", \"from\": 1958, \"to\": 1965}, {\"ngram\": \"the movies\", \"from\": 1969, \"to\": 1979}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"backflips\", \"from\": 1984, \"to\": 1994}, {\"ngram\": \"the sword\", \"from\": 2015, \"to\": 2024}, {\"ngram\": \"the air\", \"from\": 2028, \"to\": 2035}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, reality dawned when he watched the sport at the 2000 Olympics.\", \"from\": 2055, \"to\": 2126, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"reality\", \"from\": 2064, \"to\": 2071}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 2095, \"to\": 2104}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2000 Olympics\", \"from\": 2108, \"to\": 2125}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The idea of fencing started at the Sydney Olympics,\\\" said Freilich, whose parents returned to Israel from Australia in 2005.\", \"from\": 2128, \"to\": 2253, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2223, \"end\": 2229, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"score\": 0.9999999984522674, \"rank\": 1.5188605547125681e-09, \"text\": \"Israel\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\"}, {\"begin\": 2235, \"end\": 2244, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_cricket_team\", \"score\": 0.6985217505384306, \"rank\": 0.4308322280990985, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_cricket_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_cricket_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The idea\", \"from\": 2129, \"to\": 2137}, {\"ngram\": \"fencing\", \"from\": 2141, \"to\": 2148}, {\"ngram\": \"the Sydney Olympics\", \"from\": 2160, \"to\": 2179}, {\"ngram\": \"Freilich\", \"from\": 2187, \"to\": 2195}, {\"ngram\": \"whose parents\", \"from\": 2197, \"to\": 2210}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It would have been a nice way to close the circle had I got a medal here.\", \"from\": 2255, \"to\": 2329, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a nice way\", \"from\": 2275, \"to\": 2285}, {\"ngram\": \"the circle\", \"from\": 2295, \"to\": 2305}, {\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 2316, \"to\": 2323}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But I have not and I did not.\", \"from\": 2330, \"to\": 2359, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Fortunately, there are still more competitions to come.\", \"from\": 2361, \"to\": 2417, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"more competitions\", \"from\": 2391, \"to\": 2408}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hopefully next time I will be more successful.\\\"\", \"from\": 2418, \"to\": 2465, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympic dream is not yet over as Freilich has expressed a hope to keep competing until the 2032 Brisbane Games.\", \"from\": 2467, \"to\": 2582, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Olympic dream\", \"from\": 2467, \"to\": 2484}, {\"ngram\": \"Freilich\", \"from\": 2504, \"to\": 2512}, {\"ngram\": \"a hope\", \"from\": 2527, \"to\": 2533}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2032 Brisbane Games\", \"from\": 2558, \"to\": 2581}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Epee fencers can be old,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 2584, \"to\": 2619, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Epee fencers\", \"from\": 2585, \"to\": 2597}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"A few months ago I said that the plan is to go through to Brisbane.\", \"from\": 2620, \"to\": 2688, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2679, \"end\": 2687, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Gabba\", \"score\": 0.7148447492711716, \"rank\": 0.3909932717345382, \"text\": \"Brisbane\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Gabba\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Gabba\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the plan\", \"from\": 2650, \"to\": 2658}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"At the moment what I am going to do is go back to Israel, clean my room, clear my head and make the decisions.\\\"\", \"from\": 2690, \"to\": 2802, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2741, \"end\": 2747, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"score\": 0.9999999984522674, \"rank\": 1.5188605547125681e-09, \"text\": \"Israel\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the moment\", \"from\": 2694, \"to\": 2704}, {\"ngram\": \"my room\", \"from\": 2755, \"to\": 2762}, {\"ngram\": \"my head\", \"from\": 2770, \"to\": 2777}, {\"ngram\": \"the decisions\", \"from\": 2787, \"to\": 2800}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Although his first Olympic experience ended in an early exit, he insisted he was \\\"happy to be here\\\", before adding ruefully: \\\"I would have been happier for it to be a longer day.\\\"\", \"from\": 2804, \"to\": 2983, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his first Olympic experience\", \"from\": 2813, \"to\": 2841}, {\"ngram\": \"an early exit\", \"from\": 2851, \"to\": 2864}, {\"ngram\": \"a longer day\", \"from\": 2969, \"to\": 2981}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The attack on southern Israel that triggered the war resulted in the deaths of 1,197 people, mostly civilians, according to an AFP tally based on official Israeli figures.\", \"from\": 2985, \"to\": 3156, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3008, \"end\": 3014, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"score\": 0.9999999984522674, \"rank\": 1.5188605547125681e-09, \"text\": \"Israel\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\"}, {\"begin\": 3112, \"end\": 3115, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"score\": 0.9999999147128201, \"rank\": 7.532182151311305e-08, \"text\": \"AFP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\"}, {\"begin\": 3140, \"end\": 3147, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israelis\", \"score\": 0.9947917588602382, \"rank\": 0.004990122552016615, \"text\": \"Israeli\", \"types\":